healthy.rim.type

Class EN

  • java.lang.Object
    • healthy.rim.type.RimDataType
      • healthy.rim.type.EN
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class EN
extends RimDataType
    A name for a person, organisation, place or thing. A sequence of name parts, such as given name or family name, prefix, suffix, etc. Examples for entity name values are "António de Sousa Campos.", "Centro de Saude de Aveiro.", "Microsoft Corporation", etc. An entity name may be as simple as a character string or may consist of several entity name parts, such as, "António", "de Sousa", "Campos"
